      "comment": "ZIPPING BOTHAM (2) has a strong record this trip with seven wins and four placings from 21 starts. Below best last time at Wentworth Park (30.32) in a Grade 5, finishing a 9 length eighth. Expected to go close. CARUGGI (4) was strongly fancied last time on the back of a win two back but could only manage second (23.31) at Mt Gambier. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Expected to be in the finish again. EPIC STORY (3) is having his first look at this track. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 8 lengths (23.06) at Geelong. Worth following up. ",
